Package com.swordglowsblue.artifice.api

Interface ArtificeResourcePack

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, net.minecraft.resource.ResourcePack
    public interface ArtificeResourcePack
extends net.minecraft.resource.ResourcePack
    A resource pack containing Artifice-based resources. May be used for resource generation with dumpResources(java.lang.String), or as a virtual resource pack with Artifice.registerAssets(java.lang.String, com.swordglowsblue.artifice.api.util.Processor<com.swordglowsblue.artifice.api.ArtificeResourcePack.ClientResourcePackBuilder>) or Artifice.registerData(java.lang.String, com.swordglowsblue.artifice.api.util.Processor<com.swordglowsblue.artifice.api.ArtificeResourcePack.ServerResourcePackBuilder>).
